The top three sales teams refers to the teams that have generated the highest total sales amount, with the highest amount being ranked first; 
The total sales amount refers to the total value of all orders handled by each team; 
The total order changes refer to the total number of times an order has been modified.

- The 'last three months' refers to the time period from the current date back to three months ago; 
- The exchange rate is used to convert the order amount from Euros to a base currency for consistent comparison across teams;
- The revenue rank indicates the relative performance of each sales team, with '1' being the highest revenue.
